com.swirl

Class WifiInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirl.Signal
      • com.swirl.WifiInfo

  • public class WifiInfo
extends Signal
    A WifiInfo represents a wifi network access point and represents a Signal object of TYPE_WIFI. Objects of this class are created by the WifiManager in order to track changes in the users connected access point.
